{"sn46.111-120:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 46.111–120 ","sn46.111-120:0.2":"12. Esanavagga ","sn46.111-120:0.3":"Esanadisutta ","sn46.111-120:1.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, esana. ","sn46.111-120:1.2":"Katama tisso? ","sn46.111-120:1.3":"Kamesana, bhavesana, brahmacariyesana”ti vittharetabbam. ","sn46.111-120:1.4":"Esanavaggo dvadasamo. ","sn46.111-120:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn46.111-120:2.1":"Esana vidha asavo, ","sn46.111-120:2.2":"Bhavo ca dukkhata tisso; ","sn46.111-120:2.3":"Khilam malanca nigho ca, ","sn46.111-120:2.4":"Vedana tanha tasinaya cati. ","sn46.111-120:3.1":"(Bojjhangasamyuttassa esanapeyyalam vivekanissitato vittharetabbam.) "}